Google translate tokens getter ----

This module get all used tokens in translation api (batchexecute)

Types

Tokens = object
  bl*, fSid*: string
Tokens type stores the useful tokens found in Google Translate website

Procs

proc getGTokens(url: string; tld = "com"): Tokens {...}{.raises: [ValueError,
    IOError, OSError, HttpRequestError, Exception, LibraryError, SslError,
    TimeoutError, ProtocolError, KeyError, RegexError],
    tags: [ReadIOEffect, RootEffect, WriteIOEffect, TimeEffect].}

This proc access the Google translate page and gets some values

It's possible to choose a different tld for the Google translate page
